## Update User Password

Update user's password on Zoom via user ID.

> Definition

```text
POST <%= config[:api_host] %>user/updatepassword
```

> Example Request

```shell
$ curl <%= config[:api_host] %>user/updatepassword \
    -d api_key=<%= config[:ex_api_key] %> \
    -d api_secret=<%= config[:ex_api_secret] %> \
    -d id=<%= config[:ex_uuid] %>
```

> Example Response

```json
{
  "id": "<%= config[:ex_uuid] %>",
  "updated_at": "2013-09-02T12:00:00Z"
}
```

